      "text": "ja dauds/ un Moabam bija bail\npreekſch teem Iſraēta Behrneein.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz fazzija Moabs us\nteeem Midjanitern Wezzajjeem:\nNu apehdihs chi Draudse wiſſu/\nkas apkahrt mums irr/ ittin ka\nweenâ Wehrfis to Sahli wirs\nSemmes apehd; tann Laikâ bija\nBalaks/ Zipora Dehls/ to Mo-\nabiteru Rehninſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas isfuhtija Wehſtis us\nBileamu/ Beora Dehlu/ Petro-\nra/ kas pee tahs Uppes irr/ eekſch\nwinna Lauschu Behrnu Sem-\nines/ winnu aizinadains/ un fazz-\nzija: Rangi/ tur irr Laudis no\nEgiptes-Semmes iſgahjuſchi/\nreds/ tee irr to Semmes Wirfu\napktahjuſchi/ un gull man itt\npretti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nu nahz jelle/ un no-\nlahd man tohs Laudis/ jo ſchee\nirr ſtiprakine ka es/ jaschu es tohs\nwarretu apkaut/ un no tahs\nSemmes isdsiht/ jo es finnu/ ka\nkurru tu fwehti/ tas irr fwehtihts/\nun ko tu nolahdi/ tas irr no-\nlahdehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad gahje tee Moabiteru\nWezzajee/ un tee Midjanitern\nWezzajee/ un teem bija ta Sih-\nlefchanas Alga fawá Rohkâ/ un\nnahze pee Bileamu/ un runnaja\nBalaka Wahrdus us to.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas us win-\nneem: Paleezeet ſcheit pahr Nak-\nti/ tad atfazzifchn es jums/ ittin\nka tas KUNGS us mann run-\nnahs/ un tee Moaba Wirfneeki\npaliffe pee Bileama.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Deetws nahze pee Bile-\nama/ un fazzija: Kas tee tahdi\nLaudis/ kas pee tewis irr?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Bileams us\nDeewu: Balaks/ Zipora Dehls/\ntas Moabiteru Rehninſch irr pee\nman juhtijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "(Sazzidams:) Reds/\nLandis irr no Egiptes.Semmes\niſgahjuſchi/ un irr tahs Sem-\nmes Wirfu apkahjuſchi/nahz nu/\nnolahd mann tohs/ jaschu es war-\nrefchu prett teem karroht/ un tohs\nisdsiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Deetws us\nBileamn: Tew ne buhs ar win-\nxeem eet/ tew ne buhs schohs Lau-\ndis nolahdeht/ jo tee irr fivehtiti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs Bileams a-\ngri/ un fazzija us Balaka Lee-\nleem-Kungeem: Eite us juhsu\nSenumi/ jo tas KUNGS ais-\nleeds un ne palaisch mann ar\njums eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlahs tee Moaba\nWirfneeki/ un nahze pee Bala-\nku/ un fazzija: Bileams irr ais-\nleedsees ar mums eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fuhtija Balaks weh-\nwatrak/ un jo zeenigus Leelus\nKungus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee nahze pee Bileamu\nun fazzija us to: Ta ſakka ten\nBalaks/ Zipora Dehls: Ne lee\ndsees/ lubdsams! pee man nahft\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo es tew augſt gohdi\nnaschu/ un wiſſu/ ko tu us man-\nfazzifi/ darrifchu es: Tad nah-\njelle/ nolahd man fchohs Laudis\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad atbildeja Bileams\n"
    }
  ],
